title: Goran Paracki
text:
Goran Paracki (born 21 January 1987 in <a href="Pula">Pula</a>) is a <a href="Croatian%20people">Croatian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="Slaven%20Belupo">Slaven Belupo</a>.
Club career.
Wellington Phoenix.
On 20 July 2017, Paracki signed a one-year deal with <a href="Wellington%20Phoenix%20FC">Wellington Phoenix</a>.
Neftchi Baku.
On 23 June 2018, Paracki signed a one-year contract with <a href="Neft%C3%A7i%20PFK">Neftçi PFK</a>. Neftchi Baku confirmed Paracki's release on 15 May 2019.
Slaven Belupo.
On 29 June 2019, Paracki returned to <a href="Slaven%20Belupo">Slaven Belupo</a> after four years.
